<p>Best-of pages are the most powerful content format for AI citations. But only if they are built for extraction. The pages that win are not the longest or the most eloquent. They are the clearest. They lead with answers. They structure every entry as a self-contained block. They include comparison tables, quote-ready verdicts, and FAQ schema.</p>
